{"name":"Riposte","type":"advance","img":"icons/weapons/daggers/dagger-curved-purple.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.uM9hwYp4XY15niWC"}},"system":{"tier":0,"name":"","description":"<p id=\"docs-internal-guid-9d314102-7fff-79a1-e691-c9ed8caa9083\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Merriweather,serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Effect: If an enemy within your reach misses you with a melee attack: As a reaction, you can immediately make an attack against that enemy with your equipped melee weapon.</span></p>","xpCost":150,"hpBonus":1,"fpBonus":0},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1774471944879,"modifiedTime":1774471944879,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"cdL829zgn02mLeIK"}
{"name":"Lightning Reflexes","type":"advance","img":"icons/skills/movement/arrow-upward-yellow.webp","system":{"tier":3,"name":"","description":"<p><strong>Tier 3 Initiative Advance &bull; Reaction</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Prerequisites&nbsp;</strong>Initiative 7, at least two Reaction advances</p>\n<p><strong>Effect&nbsp;</strong>You may take up to two reactions per round.</p>","xpCost":600,"hpBonus":3,"fpBonus":3},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.Wi8NEemkCXm4BBSU"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1768055282827,"modifiedTime":1774471957350,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"cv3WXuhgQlfMjiD7"}
{"name":"Press the Advantage","type":"advance","img":"icons/skills/wounds/injury-pain-impaled-hand-blood.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.IATD6N6n92tkDdUx"}},"system":{"tier":1,"name":"","description":"<p id=\"docs-internal-guid-7a90fcfb-7fff-21ca-27e8-31c6acd1a6d5\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Passive, Martial, Rank 1</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">You become adept at exploiting moments of inattentiveness. You can, under certain circumstances, acquire combat advantage over your enemies. When you have combat advantage against a creature, your attacks and powers against that target become have a +2 bonus to hit; additionally, your attacks against that target gain (your tier) extra AP.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">You gain combat advantage against a creature when you are totally obscured from it, or when you are in a flanking position.</span></p>","xpCost":200,"hpBonus":2,"fpBonus":0},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1774472050625,"modifiedTime":1774472050625,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"S1q22YRDLR4pYDa5"}
